Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:09.29,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\pos(1050,170)}第12話{\fs20}\N\N{\fs60\fsp0}兩人的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我要告訴你一個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,實際上是有辦法回日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,過去 我們四大人災曾經想過要毀滅世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,其中的一個理由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,便是想要回到原本的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這個方法 是真正存在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界裡有瑪瑙在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不想回去 絕對不想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真美好的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,說得我都想要在螢幕上觀看這友情了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才的台詞 我覺得放預告篇完全夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不看片尾出演人員表的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,之後就隨你喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:01:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不等到影廳亮燈就走 我覺得是很沒禮貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 能像這樣對話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還真令人開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪瑙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那就開始最後的掙扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,預備 開拍！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,萬魔殿被這片霧抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,應該只是時間的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說只要能堅持到那時候就是我們贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 感覺沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 她的生命上限
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是她吸收的活祭品數量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只要不斷地砍 總會砍完的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前 大姐姐們的小命可能就不保了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,比力量的話 我可不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這下打得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不好啦 散架的手腳往城鎮的方向去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,正中她下懷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,殿下 請你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,落單了 好慘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,通過跟地脈連接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微補充了一點導力了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你這體質真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沒你奇怪就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,然而現在 導力並不充足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就看我能否堅持到霧把她完全吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想她一定會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但我還是想保護瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好了大家 又能跟大姐姐玩了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只用一種招數的話 觀眾可是會看膩的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,教典被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐姐 拿著這個就會變得很強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是希望你能再努力一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這下該怎麼辦呢 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這個表情 就是這個 這個表情好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,再努力一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,別認輸 要被撕成碎片了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,用那個 神官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,賣你一個人情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,亞修娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我有這個拳頭就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您的劍 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,比想像中更消耗導力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那個武器不適合大姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去會撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,到此為止了吧 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你能讓我玩得更開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,結果出乎意料地普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡結局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,到此為止了吧 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你能讓我玩得更開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,結果出乎意料地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了不要來 討厭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了 瑪瑙 用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你當自己是女主角？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不會讓你逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒有多少時間了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想讓你死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我希望你用我的導力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的力量借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不要輸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是純潔正直 而且強大的神官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真是美好的友情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我想要的是最壞的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真是比想像中簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是剛才吞下短劍的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,燈里 要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪瑙 我把我的全部都給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然能和瑪瑙連接在一起很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這個我來到這裡算是一個失敗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好瞞過去哦 我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,萬魔殿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你透過活祭品得到的生命已經用完了 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你也不能把自己的身體作為活祭品復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我讓肉體的一半以上脫離了本體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我捨棄了不死 選擇了巨大化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,為了做出一部有趣的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,向封印自己的世界復仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是享受過程哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,人災不論記憶還是人格都應該已經喪失了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會覺得讓世界陷入混亂是件快樂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因為我是「魔」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在這世間殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,引發這星球的混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,向附於此身的純粹概念立誓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,阻撓一切良善之事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以大姐姐 告訴你一個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,「白」曾揮舞過的必殺武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,「鹽之劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什麼純粹概念能都毀滅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,包括那個「時」之子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,開心嗎 還是相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,心亂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就是擾亂人心的「魔」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這下算是結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真是精彩 能解決那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不 多虧了殿下的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,況且 那只不過是一根小指
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 小指是兩手各有一根的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,確實不能說是解決了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 那孩子是異世界人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我見過她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,萬魔殿能逃出霧籠 或許是因為她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我有很多事想問
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 我也有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就放過你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,代我向桃子問好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我還活著？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是…地獄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是現實世界哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,身體感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直像是腦子被短劍穿透之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,身體又從內部爆開的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那些成為素材的人 死狀都很慘烈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,素材？是你讓我復活的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 用埋在這裡的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,重新構成了一下缺失的部分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡正好有一具異世界人的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是個超級棒的魔導素材呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子為什麼要讓我復活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪儂 你其實有一個姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是個開朗有活力 元氣滿滿的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也是個喜歡唱歌跳舞的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不過她最喜歡的 就是電影了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是失去了記憶和人格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也依然會留下些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只是在很久很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在千年前和十年前就已經結束的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我接下來 要拍一部場面更宏大的電影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你也會來幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們在這世界上掀起更巨大的混沌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你同我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是桃子 這恢復力真是不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,西西莉雅司祭都被嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為前輩一直掛念我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,對我來說 前輩的愛就是最棒的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是是 真是那樣就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,桃子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 前輩 真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我的失誤讓前輩陷入了危險的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,該道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在不清楚對方底細的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,太過依賴桃子的幫助了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有那回事 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,別太激動 你還在恢復中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說 那個人災說的是「鹽之劍」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 聽說不論什麼樣的純粹概念都能毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不覺得她是信口開河
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,「鹽之劍」的話 似乎是在離聖地不遠的西方盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,鹽之大地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前 我跟導師去過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我要再去一次那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,用「鹽之劍」殺死燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不讓她變成萬魔殿那樣可怕的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,桃子你能像之前那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,以燈里察覺不到的方式跟在我們身後嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可以…當然沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.07,0:18:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,非常謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不僅幫忙治療桃子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,還願意給我們酬勞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是因為你 還不知道損失會有多麼慘重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 憑我是解決不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,西西莉雅司祭肯定能讓城市迅速恢復和平的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你在學你導師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會 這是我的真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我最後再說句多餘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你和陽炎不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持你自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼也不要改變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,假設燈里沒殺任何人 沒造成任何傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,能保證不讓純粹概念失控的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那時我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,燈里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,醒來後找不到你 我還以為自己被丟下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是去教堂跟西西莉雅司祭打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,燈里 睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我想確認件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是真的記不得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:20:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,晚宴途中到戰鬥醒來這期間發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 完全沒印象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我救出她的時候 還有正在戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她確實是意識清醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她現在也不像在撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她並不擅長撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我不記得了 但應該讓你擔心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會再犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以拜託了 不要討厭我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你傻啊 誰會因為這種事討厭你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我是你的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快說快說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要說就趁現在說 快說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:04.62,Top,,0,0,0,,快說快說快說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…旅途的包袱…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩 不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,帥氣的處刑人前輩 我最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不能為了那個女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那種想法會讓前輩感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.72,0:21:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我要替前輩把她殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我們又要去聖地了吧 瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 做好心理準備吧 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來的旅途可是很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只要跟你在一起就沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.30,0:22:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 在一起就沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,假設燈里能保證不讓純粹概念失控的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那時我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 這不是我該想的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須趁她完全失去記憶和人格前殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我是純潔正直 而又強大的壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 我們再一起踏出第一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好好 聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.28,0:22:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,無論遇到了什麼 一定要殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,然後活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,為此我做什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.34,0:23:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是「魔」 連「器」的一部分都跑出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,自從星骸孵化後 就沒有碎片出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沒白費我一直重複個沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.41,0:23:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我第幾十次殺徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.99,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Laykarf dunon a hethkka ja
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:40.28,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dullun katre n’a sol solle flare-esta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.53,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sae que ja ton tonnu hanja
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:43.66,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ju va lerhen n’a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:58.21,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Loop through a silky ribbon, my pretender
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:02:01.68,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hide a scarlet letter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.43,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Manuals in hand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:06.51,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We paint the world a bit redder
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:11.56,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Bury my new friend, means to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.90,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Decomposing sailor shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.15,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Button down jackets, pleated skirts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.90,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:21.61,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}In the mirror I am cinderella
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:24.70,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Too late to reborn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:31.50,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If the future needs a billion samples of flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.71,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I’m your reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.96,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I’ve no colour
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:40.88,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So the least I can do for you is endure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:45.01,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We walked down the aisle unexplored
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:49.81,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We walked down the aisle unexplored
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:52.39,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Remaining strangers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:54.94,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Laykarf dunon a hethkka ja
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.07,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dullun katre n’a sol solle flare-esta
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.44,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sae que ja ton tonnu hanja
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:00.44,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ju va lerhen n’a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:58.21,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的冒牌貨繫上絲帶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:02:01.68,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}藏起深紅的信箋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.43,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿起教典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:06.51,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓我們把世界塗得更紅一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:11.56,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}埋葬我的新朋友 讓一切結束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.90,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}解開水手服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.15,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}脫下襯衫 褪去百褶裙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.90,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}穿上盛裝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:21.61,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在鏡子裡我是灰姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:24.70,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而為時已晚 已無法重生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:31.50,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果未來需要十億朵鮮花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.71,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我是你的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.96,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我失去了顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:40.88,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能為你忍受一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:45.01,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們走在無人踏足的側堂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:49.81,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們走在無人踏足的側堂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:52.39,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永遠不得相識
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:52.75,ED_JP_EP12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}静かな夢の中を　彷徨っていたあの日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:22:03.22,ED_JP_EP12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君と出会えたことで　何かが弾けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:08.52,ED_JP_EP12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}何かが動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:14.40,ED_JP_EP12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}軋む空の青を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:23.45,ED_JP_EP12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この想い伝えたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:30.66,ED_JP_EP12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3}今この瞬間を　焼き付けるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:39.50,ED_JP_EP12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur3}重ね合う手と手が　いつか離れる時まで
